#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea behind &kspaceduel; is simple, but addictive. Each of two possible "
"players controls a satellite spaceship orbiting the sun. As the game "
"progresses players have to eliminate opponent's spacecraft. As soon as the "
"opponent's satellite is destroyed, the remaining player wins the round."
msgstr ""
"Ideja za &kspaceduel; je preprosta, a zasvoji. Vsak od dveh možnih igralcev "
"nadzoruje satelitsko vesoljsko ladjo, ki kroži okoli sonca. Ko igra "
"napreduje, morajo igralci odstraniti nasprotnikovo vesoljsko plovilo. Takoj "
"ko je nasprotnikov satelit uničen, preostali igralec zmaga krog."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Destroy the opponent's satellite, while keeping the own one in tact."
msgstr "Uniči nasprotnikov satelit, svojega pa ohrani nepoškodovanega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kspaceduel; loads directly into the game mode; however, the action does not "
"start until either player makes the first move."
msgstr ""
"&kspaceduel; naloži neposredno v igralni način; vendar se akcija ne začne, "
"dokler kateri koli igralec ne naredi prve poteze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the opponent's satellite is controlled by the built in artificial "
"intelligence, game action does not start until the human player makes the "
"first move."
msgstr ""
"Če nasprotnikov satelit nadzoruje vgrajena umetna inteligenca, se igra ne "
"začne, dokler človeški igralec ne naredi prve poteze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kspaceduel; you control the ship's rotation, acceleration, and weaponry. "
"Your satellite is constantly drawn towards the sun by gravity. You have to "
"adjust the rotation and acceleration of your ship to make it stay on course."
msgstr ""
"V &kspaceduel; nadzorujete rotacijo ladje, pospešek in orožje. Vaš satelit "
"nenehno vleče proti soncu zaradi gravitacije. Prilagoditi morate vrtenje in "
"pospešek vaše ladje, da ostane v smeri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Approaching the sun too close causes the satellite to explode."
msgstr "Če se soncu približamo preblizu, satelit eksplodira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the same time you have to monitor the opponent's movement and use your "
"weapons consisting of bullets and mines, to destroy the enemy spacecraft."
msgstr ""
"Hkrati morate spremljati gibanje nasprotnika in uporabiti svoje orožje, "
"sestavljeno iz nabojev in min, da uničite sovražnikovo vesoljsko plovilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your own weapons are as harmful to your satellite as they are to the enemy "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Vaše lastno orožje je enako škodljivo za vaš satelit kot za sovražnega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kspaceduel; Game Screen Overview."
msgstr "&kspaceduel; Pregled igralnega zaslona."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kspaceduel; game screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kspaceduel; zaslon igre</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kspaceduel; game screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kspaceduel; zaslon igre</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "The top of the playing area is occupied by the menubar and toolbar."
msgstr "Na vrhu igralnega območja sta menijska in orodna vrstica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The central part of the &kspaceduel; screen is the playing area."
msgstr "Osrednji del zaslona &kspaceduel; je igralno območje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left and on the right sides of the playing area there are the Red "
"Player's and the Blue Player's information screens."
msgstr ""
"Na levi in desni strani igralnega polja sta informacijska zaslona za rdečega "
"in modrega igralca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top box on the information screen represents the <quote>Hit Points</"
"quote> of the spacecraft."
msgstr ""
"Zgornje polje na zaslonu z informacijami predstavlja <quote>točke zadetkov</"
"quote> vesoljskega plovila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The middle box on the information screen represents the battery power."
msgstr "Srednje polje na zaslonu z informacijami predstavlja moč baterije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bottom box on the information screen shows player's number of wins."
msgstr ""
"Spodnje polje na zaslonu z informacijami prikazuje igralčevo število zmag."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bottom of the playing area is the status bar."
msgstr "Na dnu igralnega območja je vrstica stanja."

