#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Energy Points"
msgstr "O energijskih točkah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each player controls one ship."
msgstr "Vsak igralec nadzoruje eno ladjo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The ships can rotate, accelerate, shoot and set mines."
msgstr "Ladje se lahko vrtijo, pospešujejo, streljajo in postavljajo mine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each ship has a limited amount of energy required for rotation, "
"acceleration, shooting and setting mines."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka ladja ima omejeno količino energije, ki je potrebna za vrtenje, "
"pospeševanje, streljanje in nastavljanje min."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each ship has a limited amount of energy."
msgstr "Vsaka ladja ima omejeno količino energije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ships absorb solar energy required for the ship's operation. The amount of "
"energy the ship gets depends on the distance from and the direction to the "
"sun."
msgstr ""
"Ladje absorbirajo sončno energijo, potrebno za delovanje ladje. Količina "
"energije, ki jo ladja prejme, je odvisna od razdalje in smeri sonca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A ship gets more energy near the sun and less energy near the border. It "
"gets the full amount of energy if the sun shines directly on the solar "
"panels and less or even no energy if the sun shines at an angle to the "
"panels or at the other side of the panels."
msgstr ""
"Ladja dobi več energije blizu sonca in manj blizu meje. Dobi polno količino "
"energije, če sonce sije neposredno na sončne panele in manj ali celo nič "
"energije, če sonce sije pod kotom na panele ali na drugo stran panelov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Bullets and Mines"
msgstr "O nabojih in minah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bullets fly around the sun just like a ship does."
msgstr "Krogle letijo okoli sonca tako kot ladja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mines have an amount of energy to stay at the same position. When the energy "
"is spent, the mines collide with the sun and disintegrate."
msgstr ""
"Mine imajo dovolj energije, da ostanejo na istem položaju. Ko se energija "
"porabi, mine trčijo ob sonce in razpadejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer to the sun the mine is set, the more energy it needs to stay in "
"place."
msgstr "Bližje kot je mina soncu, več energije potrebuje, da ostane na mestu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mines can be destroyed with bullets."
msgstr "Mine je mogoče uničiti s kroglami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default each ship has 5 bullets and 3 mines."
msgstr "Privzeto ima vsaka ladja 5 nabojev in 3 mine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Hit Points"
msgstr "O številu zadetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collision with own bullets, or enemy bullets or mines decreases the hit "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Trk z lastnimi ali sovražnimi kroglami ali minami zmanjša število zadetkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If two ships collide then the weaker ship is destroyed and the hit points of "
"the stronger ship are decreased by the amount of the hit points the weaker "
"ship had."
msgstr ""
"Če dve ladji trčita, je šibkejša ladja uničena in število zadetkov močnejše "
"ladje se zmanjša za število zadetkov, ki jih je prejela šibkejša ladja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the ship's amount of hit points goes to zero then ship explodes."
msgstr "Če število zadetkov ladje pade na nič, ladja eksplodira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a ship collides with the sun it is destroyed regardless of the amount of "
"hit points remaining."
msgstr ""
"Če ladja trči v sonce, je uničena ne glede na število preostalih zadetkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Powerups"
msgstr "Dodatki energije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "From time to time powerups appear on the play field."
msgstr "Od časa do časa se na igrišču pojavijo dodatki energije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are four different powerups:"
msgstr "Obstajajo štiri različni dodatki energije:"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mine"
msgstr "Mine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum number of mines is increased."
msgstr "Največje število min se poveča."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bullet"
msgstr "Naboj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum number of bullets is increased."
msgstr "Največje število nabojev se poveča."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Energy</guiicon> (yellow or green sphere)"
msgstr "<guiicon>Energija</guiicon> (rumena ali zelena krogla)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player's energy increases."
msgstr "Igralčeva energija se poveča."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Shield</guiicon> (red or blue sphere)"
msgstr "<guiicon>Ščit</guiicon> (rdeča ali modra krogla)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player's hit points increase."
msgstr "Število zadetkov igralca se poveča."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Starts a new game</action> of &kspaceduel;."
msgstr "<action>Začne novo igro</action> &kspaceduel;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Round</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova runda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Starts a new round</action>, at the current level."
msgstr "<action>Začne novo rundo</action> na trenutni ravni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pauses and unpauses the game."
msgstr "Začasno ustavi in obnovi igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kspaceduel;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kspaceduel;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kspaceduel;…</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kspaceduel;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a configuration dialog</action> which lets you define many "
"settings of the game, refer to the chapter <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\">Game Configuration</link> for further information."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</action>, ki vam omogoča, da "
"določite številne nastavitve igre, za nadaljnje informacije glejte poglavje "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija igre</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kspaceduel; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kspaceduel; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij "
"preberite razdelke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-"
"settings\">meniju z nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. At this moment &kspaceduel; features only one theme."
msgstr "Ne. V tem trenutku &kspaceduel; ima samo eno temo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Naredil sem napako. Ali lahko razveljavim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kspaceduel; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. &kspaceduel; nima funkcije <quote>Razveljavi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No. &kspaceduel; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature. However, if "
"you carefully read through the <link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, "
"Strategies and Tips</link> section you shouldn't have this problem."
msgstr ""
"Ne. &kspaceduel; nima funkcije <quote>Namig</quote>. Če pa natančno "
"preberete razdelek <link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Pravila igre, strategije "
"in nasveti</link>, te težave ne bi smeli imeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kspaceduel; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. &kspaceduel; nima funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248 index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Keys"
msgstr "Tipke igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kspaceduel; has a default set of keys to control the game. For a list of "
"default keys see the section entitled <link linkend=\"keys\">Default "
"Shortcuts</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kspaceduel; ima privzet nabor tipk za nadzor igre. Za seznam privzetih tipk "
"si oglejte razdelek z naslovom <link linkend=\"keys\">Privzete bližnjice</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keys can be configured by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Tipke lahko konfigurirate z izbiro menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will bring up a dialog box which lets you configure all hotkeys, "
"including the keys used for steering the space ships, for firing bullets, "
"and for laying mines."
msgstr ""
"Odprlo se bo pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko konfigurirate vse bližnjične "
"tipke, vključno s tipkami, ki se uporabljajo za krmiljenje vesoljskih ladij, "
"za izstreljevanje nabojev in za polaganje min."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see that each player (Red and Blue), has 5 keystrokes corresponding "
"to Rotate Left, Rotate Right, Accelerate, Shot, and Mines."
msgstr ""
"Vidite lahko, da ima vsak igralec (rdeči in modri) 5 tipk, ki ustrezajo "
"vrtenju v levo, vrtenju v desno, pospeševanju, strelu in minam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are finished configuring your keys, you should click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to apply your changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s konfiguracijo ključev, kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, "
"da uveljavite svoje spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to restore the default keys, simply click on the "
"<guibutton>Default</guibutton> button once. To make these changes permanent, "
"press <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obnoviti privzete tipke, preprosto enkrat kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton>. Če želite narediti te spremembe trajne, "
"pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to abandon the changes you made, and return to your previously "
"selected keys, simply click <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>, and your changes "
"will be lost."
msgstr ""
"Če želite opustiti spremembe, ki ste jih naredili, in se vrniti na predhodno "
"izbrane ključe, preprosto kliknite <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton> in vaše "
"spremembe bodo izgubljene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "All game settings of &kspaceduel; are configurable."
msgstr "Vse nastavitve igre &kspaceduel; so nastavljive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to change the game settings, simply select the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kspaceduel;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti nastavitve igre, preprosto izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kspaceduel;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will bring up a dialog box with two pages, labelled <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Game</guilabel>. The first page is rather simple, "
"the second one has seven tabs across the top."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno z dvema stranema, označenima kot "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> in <guilabel>Igra</guilabel>. Prva stran je "
"dokaj preprosta, druga pa ima na vrhu sedem zavihkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings are collected in different configurations. You can choose from "
"several pre-defined configurations."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve so zbrane v različnih konfiguracijah. Izbirate lahko med več "
"vnaprej določenimi konfiguracijami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose the <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> configuration, you can define "
"all settings for yourself."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete konfiguracijo <guilabel>Po meri</guilabel>, lahko vse nastavitve "
"določite sami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not selected <guilabel>Custom</guilabel>, you will not be able "
"to make any changes to these options."
msgstr ""
"Če niste izbrali <guilabel>Po meri</guilabel>, teh možnosti ne boste mogli "
"spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have found an interesting configuration, mail it to the author of the "
"game. It can be implemented in a future version (send the part [Game] in the "
"file <filename>~/.config/kspaceduelrc</filename>)."
msgstr ""
"Če ste našli zanimivo konfiguracijo, jo pošljite avtorju igre. Lahko se "
"implementira v prihodnji različici (pošljite del [Game] v datoteki "
"<filename>~/.config/kspaceduelrc</filename>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are finished altering the options, you should click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to apply your changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s spreminjanjem možnosti, kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, "
"da uveljavite svoje spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to restore the default, simply click on the <guibutton>Default</"
"guibutton> button once. To make these changes permanent, press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obnoviti privzeto, preprosto enkrat kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton>. Če želite narediti te spremembe trajne, "
"pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to abandon the changes you made, and return to your previous "
"options, simply click <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>, and your changes will "
"be lost."
msgstr ""
"Če želite opustiti spremembe, ki ste jih naredili, in se vrniti na prejšnje "
"možnosti, preprosto kliknite <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton> in vaše "
"spremembe bodo izgubljene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "The settings are:"
msgstr "Nastavitve so:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "The General Page"
msgstr "Splošna stran"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hit Points"
msgstr "Točke zadetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section contains two sliders allow you to define the hitpoints for each "
"of the two players; you might want to decrease the hitpoints for a player to "
"give that player a handycap."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vsebuje dva drsnika, ki vam omogočata, da določite točke zadetka "
"za vsakega od obeh igralcev; morda boste želeli zmanjšati točke zadetkov za "
"igralca, da bi temu igralcu dali handycap."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Refresh time:"
msgstr "Čas osveževanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Time between two screen refreshes in milliseconds. All other settings are "
"independent of the refresh time."
msgstr ""
"Čas med dvema osvežitvama zaslona v milisekundah. Vse druge nastavitve so "
"neodvisne od časa osveževanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Red Player</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Rdeči igralec</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section you can define whether the red player gets controlled by the "
"AI, and also choose the skill level of the AI for this player. Just "
"experiment with the different skill level to find one which fits you."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku lahko določite, ali rdečega igralca upravlja umetna "
"inteligenca, in tudi izberete raven spretnosti umetne inteligence za tega "
"igralca. Preprosto eksperimentirajte z različnimi stopnjami spretnosti in "
"poiščite tisto, ki vam ustreza."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Blue Player</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Modri igralec</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This works the same as the options for the <guilabel>Red Player</guilabel> "
"section described above."
msgstr ""
"To deluje enako kot zgoraj opisane možnosti za razdelek <guilabel>Rdeči "
"igralec</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Page"
msgstr "Stran igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can select a custom setting set from a drop-down list. Then use the "
"tabs to customize the settings a bit more."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete niz nastavitev po meri s spustnega seznama. Nato z "
"zavihki še nekoliko prilagodite nastavitve."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game speed:"
msgstr "Hitrost igre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Controls the speed of the whole game."
msgstr "Nadzoruje hitrost celotne igre."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Bullet</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Naboj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shot speed:"
msgstr "Hitrost strela:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "The speed of bullets."
msgstr "Hitrost krogel."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:325 index.docbook:357 index.docbook:389 index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energy need:"
msgstr "Potreba po energiji:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of energy needed for one shot."
msgstr "Količina energije, ki je potrebna za en strel."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:329 index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max number:"
msgstr "Največje število:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum number of bullets a player can have on the screen."
msgstr "Največje število nabojev, ki jih ima lahko igralec na zaslonu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:333 index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Damage:"
msgstr "Poškodbe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of hit points damage done when a bullet hits a ship."
msgstr "Število točk škode, ki nastane, ko krogla zadene ladjo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:337 index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Life time:"
msgstr "Življenjska doba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum life time of a bullet."
msgstr "Največja življenjska doba krogle."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:341 index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload time:"
msgstr "Čas ponovnega nalaganja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "The time a ship needs to reload a bullet."
msgstr "Čas, ki ga ladja potrebuje za ponovno polnjenje naboja."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Mine</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Mina</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mine fuel:"
msgstr "Gorivo mine:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of fuel on a mine."
msgstr "Količina goriva v mini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of energy needed for laying a mine."
msgstr "Količina energije, ki je potrebna za postavitev mine."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate time:"
msgstr "Čas aktiviranja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "The time a mine is inactive."
msgstr "Čas, ko je mina neaktivna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of hit points of damage done when a ship hits a mine."
msgstr "Število točk povzročene škode, ko ladja naleti na mino."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum number of mines a player can have on the screen."
msgstr "Največje število min, ki jih ima lahko igralec na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "The time a ship needs to reload a mine."
msgstr "Čas, ki ga ladja potrebuje za ponovno polnjenje mine."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Ship</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Ladja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration:"
msgstr "Pospešek:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration of the ships."
msgstr "Pospeševanje ladij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "The energy needed to accelerate a ship."
msgstr "Energija, potrebna za pospešek ladje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotation speed:"
msgstr "Hitrost vrtenja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "The speed at which a ship rotates."
msgstr "Hitrost, s katero se ladja vrti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "The energy needed to rotate a ship."
msgstr "Energija, potrebna za vrtenje ladje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crash damage:"
msgstr "Poškodba ob trku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of hit points damage done when two ships collide."
msgstr "Število točk škode, povzročene ob trku dveh ladij."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Sun</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Sonce</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sun energy:"
msgstr "Sončna energija:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The strength of the sun. The higher the value, the quicker ships will be "
"recharged."
msgstr "Moč sonca. Višja kot je vrednost, hitreje bodo ladje napolnjene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gravity:"
msgstr "Gravitacija:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "The strength of the gravitational pull of the sun."
msgstr "Moč gravitacijske sile sonca."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Start</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Začetek</guilabel>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Position X:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Position Y:</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Položaj X:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Položaj Y:</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ships position at the beginning of a new round. The ships start at "
"opposite sides of the sun."
msgstr ""
"Ladje se postavijo na začetek nove runde. Ladje štartajo na nasprotnih "
"straneh sonca."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Velocity X:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Velocity Y:</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Hitrost X:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Hitrost Y:</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Velocity at the beginning of a new round."
msgstr "Hitrost na začetku nove runde."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Powerups</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Dodatki energije</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance time:"
msgstr "Čas nastopa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximal time between the appearance of two powerups."
msgstr "Največji čas med pojavoma dveh dodatkov energije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximal life time of a powerup."
msgstr "Največja življenjska doba dodatka energije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energy amount:"
msgstr "Količina energije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount of energy a player gets from an energy powerup."
msgstr "Količina energije, ki jo igralec pridobi z dodatno energijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shield amount:"
msgstr "Količina ščita:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount of hit points a player gets from a shield powerup."
msgstr "Količina točk zadetkov, ki jih igralec dobi z okrepitvijo ščita."

